##The epidemic brought me out of the closet

Gayspot

Feature Introduction, Independent magazine, focus on the existence and survival of sexual minorities.

Interview, Essay | Zhao Li

A cotton face mask that my mother cleaned repeatedly

On January 31st, just after 5:00 a.m. , the force woke up. He could hear the rustling of the mother next door getting out of bed.

He knew his father would be the first one out of the House after 7:00. He is going to the county by bike. My father, who did not work in the county's health department, had been going out every day since Jan. 26 to check on the outbreak of pneumonia caused by the COVID-19, to see if any of the businesses were still operating secretly, if anyone was leaving the house without a mask. "CAN NOT HARM ONESELF HARM OTHERS SA! " The father most loves to say this sentence to have the use.

At about nine o'clock, my mother would go out. Mother was not working, his father entrusted her to find a job in the county labor dispatch, but because of the epidemic, the mother can not go to work temporarily. The mother was restless, and the tall, thin mother was not only a good worker, she was now picketing the village four or five times a day, along with several other men and women who were also sent to work in the county.

"I'm going out, the rice is in the pot, and you can heat it up yourself, " my mother said, raising her voice to the force on the second floor as she went out, wearing a mask, "I should have come back earlier today. The two Mahjong players we caught yesterday should not have dared to play today. "

Back from Wuhan

On January 23rd, when the news of the closure of Wuhan came, the force was not so nervous. On the contrary, the subsequent Xiaogan City, let the four members of the Wu family have some panic. Buke lives in a village under the jurisdiction of the city of Xiaogan. Usually the New Year, the village elders laugh at the children called the most lively. These two days the people in the village are also Zhang Parents Li family to and fro a short visit. A day later, the village council issued a ban on random access, and began arranging for its party members to be on duty at the only two entrances. "We can't control the little roads leading into the fields, " said mother.

"You mustn't say that you are back from Wuhan, " the father of the force that day home after exhorting force, "this is very serious. "

"What's the matter? " And Sister Wu Chun cooking mother heard his father's words, feel his expression is very dignified.

"This time it's serious. I don't want people to judge us. Just don't go out and say you're back from Wuhan. " My father rapped the table with his hand.

Force has been lowered head, pretending to brush the appearance of mobile phones, dare not look up at his father. If my father knew that he had gone to Wuhan with his boyfriend for four days, he would probably skin himself. He began to like the same sex since junior high school, became his own inner oppression of a boulder. At this time, and a Wuhan.

That night, he returned to his room and videotaped his boyfriend. "This outbreak is scary. Do you have any signs? " The boyfriend did not, but he was clearly frightened. "How many days have we been apart? " He counted by force. "three days. " The boyfriend was distraught. "I have to go. "

And the violence began to wear off. The young men, still in their third year of college, traveled to many bustling places, Yellow Crane Tower, Hankou's business district, the Wuhan University, the airport, the train station... as he leafed through them, he recalled the journey over the past few days, i even tried to delete all the photos from my phone in the end.

The Random Thoughts of force was interrupted by the cry of her sister, Wu Chun. "Why do you want me to go back? " My sister asked loudly. "Keep your voice down, " there was a trace of supplication and forbearance in her mother's tone. "It's for the good of our family! " "It's for the good of the three of you! " Her sister's voice was hoarse with sobs.

Wu Chun was short, not tall like his parents or a fighter. Because Wu Chun has been malnourished since he was a child. Especially after the family gave birth to her younger brother's force, she was sent to her grandmother's house, eat worse, the body is also worse, every time the flu can be hard to catch her. Even so, the parents or the good use of food to the force, but also teach Wu Chun to take good care of his younger brother.

Force has always felt sorry for Wu Chun, in order to escape, even the university did not stay in the province, but ran to the north. But Wu Chun did not read university, high school after graduation in the parents'request to go to work, and even every New Year will give force a lucky money. "Even my parents do not give me lucky money, but my sister to me. " Force a thought of this, nose and acid. He cries a lot.

January 24th, 6:00 a.m. , Force Awakens. Turning his head, he saw a red envelope lying beside his pillow. It contained three thousand yuan. Force immediately understand what, wearing down jacket, barefoot, ran to his sister's bedroom. Sure enough, there was no one inside.

"My elder sister? " Force runs to the bedroom of parents, discover also nobody. I'm the only one in the house! Force. That's when the panic started. Hurry up and call Wu Chun. After a few rings, Ms. Wu answered the phone, and in a cacophony of voices, she said, "brother, my sister is not home for the New Year this year. My parents sent me to the train station. " "where are you going? " She asked, forcefully and subconsciously. "Back to the factory. " Wu Chun choked up, "you and your parents at home for a good year. "

Boyfriend information

The force is really angry. He barricaded himself in his bedroom. Parents do not seem to know, after returning from the train station, happily preparing New Year's Eve dinner, but also turned on the television very loud.

"They sent my sister away, " force told her boyfriend. "They said it was my sister who came back from Wuhan, not me. I hope that would be a cover. " With that, force leaned against the wall, his head raised, his eyes red. The boyfriend simply told him not to think about it. But the words are too weak. It hurts to use force. He didn't understand why. Until the TV set sounded the happy Voice of the Spring Festival gala, his mother called him downstairs, he did not awkwardly downstairs.

Mother knew when she saw the look of force. She took a few steps up the stairs and came up, whispering, "don't make your father angry. It's New Year's Day! "

"You all know is the new year, but also let my sister back to the factory. " The force whispered back to his mother.

"still not your good deed! " The mother seemed to be angry, "if you go home on vacation, do not go to Wuhan toss about, there can be such a thing? You have not been to Wuhan, must go again this year Baba! " The Mother did not want to argue with force, she turned to go downstairs to the kitchen, only a few steps, she suddenly remembered what, "you go with WHO Wuhan? " Asked Meng Di, the force did not react, suddenly choked. My father called out to my mother from the kitchen, and my mother hurried over.

Force to Wu Chunfa Video, "sister, how do you give me lucky money? I am 21 years old, is not a child! "

Wu Chun has arrived at the dormitory of the factory. She smiled, "today when I left, they brought me a lot of things! There is meat, ribs, vegetables, and I love to eat shrimp, I am cooking to eat! " And let the force see.

The hanging heart of force is released. He peered into the kitchen, where his parents were still cooking. He dialed the video to his boyfriend. The boyfriend pressed the button and didn't answer. After a long time, he sent a message, "I'm not in a good mood. I haven't told my parents about my visit to Wuhan the other day. But I think they will know soon. If I have an epidemic, I hope my parents are OK. It is said that people will die from it. "

The force originally has some relaxed mood, was the boyfriend this sentence again irritably raised the throat.

We're out of masks

On January 25th the village's firecrackers seemed less deafening than in previous years. Lying on the bed by force. After ten o'clock, the father unexpectedly opened the door and came in. "Do you have a fever? " He said, leaning his hand out.

The force was startled. "No fever. " He stepped aside. Force is not used to always say the father suddenly so "warm. ".

"nothing good. " The father stood up straight, left the bed of force, "hurry up! This is what time! Even if the holiday, so lazy, should not! "

After father goes out, force gave Wu Chun to send a 520 yuan red envelope. Wu Chun wouldn't take it back. Force gave an ultimatum, "you do not accept, I do not want your lucky money after! " Wu Chun then received, "there was no one in the factory, just me and a few colleagues who didn't go home. We agreed to play cards later. You don't have to worry about me. Tell Mom and dad I'm fine. "

My father was notified on the afternoon of the first day of the Lunar New Year and asked to work from the second day. Mother called force down the stairs, "you buy some masks. "

The force won't go. It's taking too long. The mother couldn't help speaking loudly. "If your sister were here, she would be out by now. Could you hurry up? " Force didn't want to talk back, and silently put on a down jacket.

It's a small village with one pharmacy, three mini-supermarkets and a delivery point. On the shelves of the drugstore were only six face masks, three cotton styles, and three disposable medical masks. She looked at him with force. "Isn't there another mask? "

"Are you the younger son of the Wu Family? " The shopkeeper's mother is supposed to be enthusiastic. "We don't have much in stock. It's said that you can't even buy masks in Wuhan now. There are only a few. Do you still want them? "

The force ponders a bit, fumbles the handset, on the net also has the goods. He was surprised that there were no masks on the Internet! He was so busy that he bought it all for fifteen dollars. It was supposed to be $16, but the owner's mother wiped out a dollar for him.

He was too embarrassed to leave and bought two more bottles of alcohol. Later, the father praised, "after all, people who went to college think better than us. " Over the next few days, the two bottles of alcohol were used to sterilize the violent parents.

Back home, force told his mother about the experience of buying masks. Mother was very nervous. "You'd better not go out. Stay at home for a few days. Don't let others see you. "

The lipstick mask my sister threw away

I have secrets, too

Since January 26, the violence of being told to stay at home by her mother has been extremely stifling, apart from watching her broadcast to the village twice a day, "NO NEW YEAR GREETINGS! No Mahjong! NO CARDS! No dinners! No treats! Stay at home! Go out and wear a mask! " Most of the time, he just walked up and down the stairs of his house.

The boyfriend only video-chats with himself occasionally. Instead, Wu Chun, and he talked for half an hour every day, "you don't worry about me, you pay more attention to yourself, after all, you live at home, I am nothing in the factory. "

On January 29, force didn't know what he was thinking, and the words came out of his mouth, "sister, if I like boys, can you accept that? " Later, he thought to himself, he should see the daily increase in the number of infections and deaths, made him finally afraid. "It's the fear that no one will ever know who they really are until they die, " explained force and her boyfriend.

Hearing this, Wu Chun was shocked at the end of the camera. Then his voice suddenly became loud and he called out the name of the force directly. "Don't make a scene! My parents had to leave home in order to give birth to you. They also fined me. You can't do this! "

The force listens to Wu Chun so finish saying, secretly blame oneself, should not so easily told elder sister. Even if you feel sorry for your sister, you shouldn't tell the truth. Now it's a problem, because my sister clearly can't handle the fact that she's Gay. Moreover, the force does not know exactly how Wu Chun thinks. Now everywhere is closed, sister is not there is no way to ask others to understand the same situation? The more I think about it, the more I don't know what to do with it, so I text my boyfriend. Boyfriend slowly, a half-day back to a, "you say before how do not think clearly? " Force did not expect the boyfriend would say so.

At this point the force felt like the most dear sister and just together no six months boyfriend "betrayed" . The force thinks in the mind, is oneself come out to elder sister, be for oneself? Yes and no. The force feels like it's divided into three people.

The first person is himself, he wants to live free and easy, in this father said the family, he does not always have to act like what.

The second one was for a boyfriend. Although the force knew that the boyfriend will not come out of the closet, his parents are old, and is that kind of stuffy people. Although the two people together for a short time, but the force always want to try to go longer. What the military didn't realize was that, in a situation like this, telling your boyfriend that you're out of the closet only seems to stress him more, not make him feel safer. But force is only 21 years old.

The last person, force in the bottom of my heart has a very small voice, I hope sister Wuchun understand, they do not look so easy happiness, at least there is pain, there is a secret. But the sister didn't think it was his pain, it was her pain.

The more I thought about the force, the more bored, sent a friend circle, "now love, perhaps more than a year, has been considered to grow old together. "

He wanted to tell his sister something

By the time mother came back, the force was asleep. When he woke up, he found his mother had washed her mask and hung it on a rope tied between the stairs on the first floor and the kitchen, where aprons and coats usually hung.

Force is very surprised, "mom, this mask can not wash it! "

Mother heard the words of force, from the kitchen out, "do not wash how to use? Now everywhere to buy do not wear a mask. "

"Then don't go out, stay at home! " said the force.

Mother wouldn't let me, "Your father goes out every day, and I'm worried that if I'm here all day, I'll be Random Thoughts. Might as well get out of the house every day. In fact, the people in the village are almost know, love playing Mahjong on a few, do not need to go out every day! That is, to find something to do and be distracted."The mother, who had been talking for a long time, seemed a little embarrassed, "hurriedly asked,"hungry, I will cook for you to eat

Force shook his head, "I go a little farther away from the pharmacy, see if there are selling masks. "

Mother smiled, "you do not go out is to save the mask. I usually wash, this old-fashioned cotton mask still works. " Force nose acid. Only then did he realize that the affection between his parents seemed to be the model of love he had been looking for and looking forward to.

Mother went into the kitchen and began to prepare dinner. Force to see the time, father from the county back, riding a bicycle almost thirty minutes. He went back to his bedroom to think. Force had to admit, his sister Wuchun is not good. On the 30th day of the Lunar New Year, when my parents were worried that others would know that they had returned from Wuhan, and I asked my sister to tell me that she had gone to Wuhan to play and was now leaving the village, why couldn't I stand up a little bit? Can I at least say something to make my sister feel better.

And at this time although the force can comfortably lie at home, but more afraid is, sister Wuchun will also because of so many years of Grievance, tell their true situation at home? But to force their own initiative to go to their parents, this is harder for him. "maybe later! " The force promised to itself, "but not now. "

On the night of January 30th, when my father returned home, there was a gleam of joy in his exhaustion, "We walked a lot today, and our masks are wet. We don't sell them anywhere. Luckily, the county gave everyone a bag of masks. They said they would give them back when they ran out. " Place a bag of disposable surgical masks in a clear plastic bag on the table. "You two can use them, too. Once you're out of the house, wear masks! "

In the evening when having dinner, everybody as a rule asked each other whether have a fever, cough. Especially Wu Chun, mother will call Wu Chun every day. For some reason that day, my mother put me on speakerphone. In the past, the force would have been very active to talk to Wu Chun, but that day he was too nervous to speak. And Wu Chun's tone sounded the same as always. Until finally, if not the mother said "force also and elder sister speak, " I am afraid that the two sisters will not call each other.

Mother seemed to sense something, hung up the phone and asked force, "you two quarrel? " Force shook his head, I think, more difficult than fighting. He found that he did not trust his sister, for fear that Wu Chun would "harm" himself.

Until February 2, force and boyfriend has left Wuhan 13 days, no symptoms. The two began video chatting more and more, three or four times a day for half an hour each time. The boyfriend's face and voice became lighter and lighter, occasionally joking. But the force knows that there is a little crack, if not the slightest, in his relationship with his boyfriend. In his view, two people in the previous two days of telephone, each other is more concerned about their own feelings, rather than each other. He didn't know if it was because the outbreak was too serious, or if the relationship hadn't lasted long enough.

As for Wu Chun, force still does not have the courage to contact. And Wu Chun didn't contact him. Force can only wait. Let Force fear is, the more quiet Wu Chun, the more he is not in the heart, the elder sister will be their own secret as a secret, or will tell the parents? Or become the sister in turn to blackmail their own weight? But the "fear" of force, and let him feel some sorry for his sister so many years to pay.

But there's something the force wants to tell her sister.

After dinner on Feb. 2, he helped his mother pack up and asked her casually, "why do I have to let my sister leave? In fact, no one knows I came back from Wuhan until now. "

Mother back to force, busy, "We all know you are from Wuhan Back Ah! So let the spring sister left, once we unfortunately infected, at least she was less likely to be infected. "

An acid in the nose of force. Maybe this is his family, plain and simple. In any case, even if the current epidemic, many people choose to let others understand the appearance of difficult, but life will continue, family is always difficult to cut off.
